# Stray Obsidian notes at the vault root (repo root doubles as the Obsidian
# vault, so personal notes can land here). Only these root-level docs are tracked:
/*.md
!/README.md
!/CLAUDE.md
!/ADMIN-GUIDE.md
!/PORTAL-CONTENT-SPEC.md
